s up to €35 million or 7% of global revenue."]}],["$","br","4",{}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["For enterprises deploying autonomous AI agents, three requirements stand out:"]}],["$","br","6",{}],["$","h2","7",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"1. Transparency"}],["$","br","8",{}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Article 13:"}]," High-risk AI systems must be designed to ensure their operation is sufficiently transparent to enable users to interpret the system's output and use it appropriately."]}],["$","br","10",{}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"What this means for agents:"}]," Every agent action must be explainable. Why did the agent do this? What policy allowed it? Who approved it?"]}],["$","br","12",{}],["$","p","13",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"How Vienna OS addresses it:"}]," The governance pipeline records the full decision chain — intent, policy evaluation, risk tier assignment, approval status, and warrant issuance. Every action has a provable explanation."]}],["$","br","14",{}],["$","h2","15",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"2. Human Oversight"}],["$","br","16",{}],["$","p","17",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Article 14:"}]," High-risk AI systems shall be designed and developed so that they can be effectively overseen by natural persons."]}],["$","br","18",{}],["$","p","19",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"What this means for agents:"}]," Humans must be able to intervene, approve, or reject agent actions before they execute — especially for high-risk actions."]}],["$","br","20",{}],["$","p","21",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"How Vienna OS addresses it:"}]," Risk-tiered approval workflows. T0 actions auto-approve (low risk). T1/T2 actions require explicit operator approval before a warrant is issued. Operators can intervene at any point in the pipeline."]}],["$","br","22",{}],["$","h2","23",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"3. Record-Keeping"}],["$","br","24",{}],["$","p","25",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"Article 12:"}]," High-risk AI systems shall be designed with capabilities enabling the automatic recording of events (logs) over the lifetime of the system."]}],["$","br","26",{}],["$","p","27",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"What this means for agents:"}]," Complete, immutable audit trails of every agent action, decision, and outcome."]}],["$","br","28",{}],["$","p","29",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"text-white font-semibold","children":"How Vienna OS addresses it:"}]," Append-only audit ledger. Every event is permanently recorded — proposals, policy decisions, warrants, executions, verifications, and anomalies. Data is retained for 7+ years."]}],["$","br","30",{}],["$","h2","31",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Beyond Compliance"}],["$","br","32",{}],["$","p","33",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["The EU AI Act sets a floor, not a ceiling. Enterprises that adopt governed AI execution don't just satisfy regulators — they build operational confidence."]}],["$","br","34",{}],["$","p","35",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["When your board asks \"how do we control our AI agents?\", the answer shouldn't be \"we hope the guardrails work.\" It should be \"every action is governed, warranted, verified, and audited.\""]}],["$","br","36",{}],["$","h2","37",{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Getting Started"}],["$","br","38",{}],["$","p","39",{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed my-2","children":["Vienna OS maps directly to EU AI Act requirements. If you're deploying agents in or serving the EU market, governance isn't optional — it's the law."]}],["$","br","40",{}],["$","hr","41",{"className":"border-navy-700 my-8"}],["$","br","42",{}],["$","p","43",{"className":"text-slate-400 italic text-sm mt-6","children":"Start governing your agents today. Free tier available →"}],["$","br","44",{}]]}],["$","$Lf",null,{"slug":"eu-ai-act-agent-compliance"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12","children":["$","$L10",null,{"variant":"compact","showSocialProof":true,"className":"max-w-lg mx-auto"}]}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"border-t border-navy-700 py-8 mt-12","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition mb-4","children":[["$","svg",null,{"ref":"$undefined","xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4","children":[["$","path","1l729n",{"d":"m12 19-7-7 7-7"}],["$","path","x3x0zl",{"d":"M19 12H5"}],"$undefined"]}],"Back to Blog"]}],["$","div",null,{"classNa